name: Leetcode Online Judge Alfred Workflow
tagline: This is a simple search workflow for Alfred 2
body:
Enjoy the workflow and good luck!

1. Import the workflow to your Alfred 2 app. (Already bought the [Power Pack](http://www.alfredapp.com/powerpack/))
2. Search start by 'lt' with the word you want to search
![Screenshot](https://github.com/dudnju/-LeetcodeWF/blob/master/sc_wf.png?raw=true)
3. Go to the question you want in the result list

Download:
[click me](https://github.com/dudnju/-LeetcodeWF/blob/master/Leetcode%20OJ%20v1.alfredworkflow?raw=true)
